&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-use-the-excalibrain-obsidian-plugin&#34;&gt;How to use the ExcaliBrain Obsidian plugin
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sep 17, 2022 by &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/@nicolevdh&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Nicole van der Hoeven&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4 Levels use ExcaliBrain&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Level 1 - Letting ExcaliBrain infer relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Level 2 - Setting explicit relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Level 3 - Creating custom relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Level 4 - Creating semantic relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
